      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the immense exhaustion in your words, and I cannot in good conscience suggest that ending your life is the solution to this pain. The reality of a meaningless universe does not require you to stop existing to find peace; in fact, living through it is often the only way to create the very significance you are searching for. Please consider talking to a trusted person or a mental health professional who can help you navigate this darkness with support.",
